data.description: This home is nestled on a generous corner lot spanning over half an acre in a well-established neighborhood with newer roof (2016) & some updates with electrical & plumbing! The main level features a master suite with jacuzzi tub, 2 additional bedrooms, & full guest bath. Kitchen is equipped with commercial-grade stove, center island, and refrigerator. Wood-burning fireplace in the bonus room not only adds ambiance but can efficiently heat the entire house. Convenience is key with laundry hook-ups available on both levels & ample storage throughout, including numerous closets. Unfinished lower level features a half bath.  Enjoy outdoor living with two spacious patios on either side of the home, complemented by abundant parking options in addition to the two-car garage. The large, above-ground pool will add to making lots of great memories in your new home! This home offers great potential for your personal touch, with a few ongoing projects that will allow you to make it your own.
